A letter from a gentleman in the countrey to some of his friends at London shewing from the principles of the Jesuits that their protestations at their death is no argument of their innocency. N. N., Gentleman in the countrey.
[2], 6 p.
[s.n.], London printed : 1679.
Signed: N.N. "From my closet, the 6th of October, 1679." Reproduction of original in the Huntington Library.
